-- Payments processor Wex to buy peer Evolution1 for $532.5 mln
-- By Abhirup Roy in Bangalore
-- Mon Jun 16, 2014 04:34PM EDT
-- None



June 16 (Reuters) - Payment processor Wex Inc <WEX.N> said it would buy privately held peer Evolution1 for $532.5 million in cash to strengthen its position in the healthcare payment processing market.

The deal, expected to close in the third quarter, would be funded through cash on hand and existing credit facility, Wex said in a statement on Monday. [ID:nBw9pcdZCa]